	quest.71151BB59F5C2307.title: "Find Petrol"
	quest.712A93B1E8B43823.quest_subtitle: "A &6Packager&r will pack items from the connected inventory into a package when given &credstone&r power"
	quest.714382D8E9E06DB7.quest_subtitle: "Beam Reader: display the properties of the incoming beam."
	quest.7159CFA999673677.quest_subtitle: "Made by mixing Gold and Copper Ingots with a Blaze Burner."
	quest.72198C23A0D07A3B.quest_subtitle: "A clutch that uncouples after a set delay when the network is overstressed. Can be reset with a wrench."
	quest.72198C23A0D07A3B.title: "Obtain Overstress clutch"
	quest.726800AC7F7C161F.quest_subtitle: "A bulkier version of the Spyglass"
	quest.72C5E74B15EFB67A.quest_subtitle: "Copy your written book, enchanted book, name tag, train schedule and more. Consumes experience for enchanted books, and squid ink sacs for most other recipes."
	quest.72C5E74B15EFB67A.title: "&6Craft Printer."
	quest.72F3965D09F3B6F0.quest_desc: ["You can press &eU&r on the &fStraw&r to see what liquids it accepts, as well as their burn times"]
	quest.72F3965D09F3B6F0.quest_subtitle: "Ever wanted to pipe liquids into your &6Blaze Burners&r? Just hand them a &fStraw&r and they'll slurp it straight from the pipe!"
	quest.73A2838E56534342.quest_subtitle: "A &6Portable Fluid Interface&r allows contraptions to transfer fluids to blocks"
	quest.73CA3C62CBC41E94.quest_subtitle: "This machine simplifies channeling setups."
	quest.73CA3C62CBC41E94.title: "Activate the Encased Fan with a Conduit Cage"
	quest.7452A3A5599B09AB.quest_desc: ["One thing not mentioned by &b&lponder&r is that the funnel can drop items on the ground when placed on an inventory and will only keep one item on the ground if it's close enough to the block the item lands on"]
	quest.7452A3A5599B09AB.quest_subtitle: "A &6Funnel&r allows input and output of inventories one item at a time"
	quest.746028A444AF32BB.title: "Materials for Flanged Cogwheels and Transmission Chain"
