	quest.75A28517E08FE190.title: "Serious Organization"
	quest.75BA8D3D6C0B9D1C.quest_subtitle: "The Basket and Cutting Board can be supported by the Mechanical Arm and Mechanical saw to manage numerous tasks, including supplying ingredients and cooking."
