	quest.763C356859F85A65.quest_subtitle: "First step is to saw and press a tumbaga sheet to create the head casing, then you will then need to imbue the head with the effects of fire resistance and regeneration. When that is done, a tumbaga alloy is used to seal the potions and add the iconic nose, finishing the totem head."
	quest.76685EA6C13CDC38.quest_subtitle: "They can be used as a light source or for crafting."
	quest.76685EA6C13CDC38.title: "Obtain Prismarine Crystals"
